728341f-a.title: Richmond: Annadale Road - Sneden Avenue
728341f-a.text:
(1)
Annadale Road, south of the S.E. corner of Sneden Ave. The
two houses stand on the M. Rice property (1898 and 1907 maps).
May 4, 1926.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
A view of the first house seen in view 1, looking northward
toward Sneden Ave.
May 4, 1926.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

729672f-a.title: Richmond: Sneden Avenue - Annadale Road
729672f-a.text:
Sneden Ave. (houses thereon), south side, east from Annadale
Road to Barclay Ave. The view is southeastward across the tracks of
the Staten lIsland Railroad.
1924.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
